\@writefile{lof}{\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {12}{\ignorespaces L-shape pipeline with unit-disk target. The six L-corners are marked in red; proportional-arc Tutte (\subref  {fig:l-ci-tutte}) places them around the circle at positions proportional to their L-perimeter arc-length. No artificial corner alignment; the Winslow output (\subref  {fig:l-ci-winslow}) is valid ($\min I = 0.17$, $\max \eta = 4.29$) and more than $2.5\times $ better in $\max \eta $ than the square-target output of Figure\nobreakspace  {}\ref {fig:l-square-pipeline}.\relax }}{19}{figure.caption.23}\protected@file@percent }
\newlabel{fig:l-circle-pipeline}{{12}{19}{L-shape pipeline with unit-disk target. The six L-corners are marked in red; proportional-arc Tutte (\subref {fig:l-ci-tutte}) places them around the circle at positions proportional to their L-perimeter arc-length. No artificial corner alignment; the Winslow output (\subref {fig:l-ci-winslow}) is valid ($\min I = 0.17$, $\max \eta = 4.29$) and more than $2.5\times $ better in $\max \eta $ than the square-target output of Figure~\ref {fig:l-square-pipeline}.\relax }{figure.caption.23}{}}
